short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Colab Monkey brings chatGPT to Google Colab. Making you the fastest coder in the jungle.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Colab Monkey is your ultimate coding companion, transforming Google Colab with the power of generative AI, much like Copilot but tailored for the Google Colab environment. It's designed to make you the fastest coder in the jungle by seamlessly integrating chatGPT into your coding workflow. Getting started is simple: download the Chrome Extension, enter your OpenAI API key, and open Google Colab. To execute a command, just write it down and press Shift+Alt+Enter (Alt is Option on Mac).
